{"tid":368454,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【世大運直擊】何詩蓓100自首名闖決賽明衝金 杜敬謙200混再破港績晉級","createTime":"2017-08-21T14:22:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T15:32:53.000Z","uid":6762,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"549ff86e53eb8f48680a1343fcde26ecad9da5d0","tid":368454,"uid":6762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:22:26.000Z","msg":"【體路台北直擊】兩位香港人氣泳手何詩蓓（Siobhan）及杜敬謙（Kenneth）今晚（21日）在「2017台北世界大學運動會」繼續發威！何詩蓓在女子100米準決賽以第1名強勢晉級決賽，明晚（22日）全力衝擊香港第1金；杜敬謙亦不讓專美，於男子200米混合泳準決賽再破港績，以第8名躋身決賽，接捧爭牌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i1.wp.com/sportsroad.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2017taipeiuniversiade_swimming_day1_20170820-07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fsportsroad.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F08%2F2017taipeiuniversiade_swimming_day1_20170820-07.jpg&h=b437baaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今早以55秒18排總成績第3位晉級的何詩蓓，在100米自由泳第2組準決賽發揮出應有水平，頭50米分段時間為26秒13，最終游出54秒52，縱未能再締個人最佳時間，仍以總成績第1名殺入明晚8時20分舉行的決賽，強勢衝擊香港首面金牌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i2.wp.com/sportsroad.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2017taipeiuniversiade_swimming_day2_kennethto_20170821-02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fsportsroad.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F08%2F2017taipeiuniversiade_swimming_day2_kennethto_20170821-02.jpg&h=3da895b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i1.wp.com/sportsroad.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2017taipeiuniversiade_swimming_day2_kennethto_20170821-06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fsportsroad.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F08%2F2017taipeiuniversiade_swimming_day2_kennethto_20170821-06.jpg&h=3bebe6fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男子200米混合泳方面，早上在初賽已做出2分02秒41刷新香港紀錄的杜敬謙，出戰第1組準決賽，頭100米一直領先，雖然及後被兩位俄羅斯及一位英國泳手超前，不過他依然以2分01秒37再締新猷，連同第2組準決賽成績，一日兩破紀錄的Kenneth剛好以第8名取得決賽一席位，明晚8時25分亮相力爭三甲獎牌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://sportsroad.hk/archives/162881\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsportsroad.hk%2Farchives%2F162881&d=T5GqAMoknpQKFzmuFUSIu%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=be433518\" target=\"_blank\">http://sportsroad.hk/archives/162881</a>"},{"pid":"595e3da139316aad98a725d4d3dcb58808b79b7a","tid":368454,"uid":561,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T23:12:51.000Z","msg":"香港勁抽<br />\n過兩日去睇籃波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f55d002228e9d20131752d3a4cd0ebf413f79f","tid":368454,"uid":71758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T23:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22e73040fb065a5e25947f352b0e6045c264ad4c","tid":368454,"uid":32527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T15:32:53.000Z","msg":"拎金都冇人理呀 仲講乜撚野本土文化 港獨呀<br />\n食撚屎啦腥港人"}]}